dataIdInfo.idPurp: General vegetation cover of Sedgwick Reserve, June 2017, intended to support reserve management and research planning.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Land cover of Sedgwick Reserve and immediate surrounds was mapped using 7.5m resolution AVIRIS imagery acquired in June 2017. Ten landcover classes were mapped based on dominant canopy composition using a random forest classifier with training samples acquired at the reserve during 2017 and 2018.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Gabriel Daldegan, UCSB Department of Geography
